[h4 id=Stage2FestivalPass 
	" Stage 2 Festival Pass
	$LF
]h4
[pre 
	$LF
]pre
[p 
	"MidAir Jumping saves frames at some places. Also an enemy moving right helps Ponta move more quickly to right when Ponta is on it. Ponta does a special performance by Mid-Air Jumping while he fights the boss of the stage. The boss never dies unless Ponta gets an item from the boss. But if Ponta beats it very quickly, it drops the item inside blocks and the item goes out of the screen.
	$LF
]p
[pre 
	$LF
]pre
[h4 id=Stage3LakeKurekappa 
	" Stage 3 Lake Kurekappa
	$LF
]h4
[pre 
	$LF
]pre
[p 
	"Just before encountering the boss of the stage, Ponta goes into a small pond and gets to the boss by way of under the ground. After attacking the boss, it is invincible until it jumps and lands on the ground. Therefore, leading the boss to the highest ground is the best way to beat it quickly. To do so, Ponta faints away on the highest ground when the life of the boss leaves two, releasing Hinako to have her attack the boss there.
	$LF
]p
[pre 
	$LF
