[p 
	"Ponta shoots at an empty place once before getting to the final boss. It looks like a miss, but the purpose of the shooting is to keep some enemy from appearing. Before beating the boss, Ponta releases Hinako and steps forward a bit to lead her to the ideal place.   Then I finish inputting keys. Hinako beats the boss automatically.
]p
